[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+    284[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [38;2;235;203;139m**[38;2;235;203;139mOverlap: Networking (VPC endpoints) and Security (KMS-via-endpoint).[38;2;235;203;139m**[K
[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+    285[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [38;2;192;197;206mThe KMS encryption posture in the security section requires the KMS VPC endpoint in the networking section. Treated as a coupled pair; addressing one without the other yields a non-functional private-subnet deployment.[K
