[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+    295[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [38;2;192;197;206mTwo CRITICAL findings auto-fail the recipe per the review rubric. The critical issues are not structural design flaws; they are (1) a clinical inconsistency that is fixable with a small rewrite of either the Problem narrative or the Sample Output, and (2) a compliance gap in SMS delivery that is fixable by shifting to a notification-plus-portal-link pattern or adding an explicit consent/content-limitation section. Both fixes are well-scoped and leave the recipe's core architecture and teaching value intact.[K
