[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+    297[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [38;2;192;197;206mThree HIGH findings (VPC endpoints, IAM scoping, Bedrock model-invocation-logging PHI) are the same recurring Chapter 2 pattern that has appeared across 2.2, 2.3, 2.4 reviews. These are production-hardening gaps, not design flaws. The MEDIUM findings (bounded regeneration, Step Functions HITL pattern, idempotency, Guardrails capability description, sample-output provenance completeness, PHI minimization in prompts) are meaningful but tractable. The LOW findings are polish items.[K
